promptPrefix:
[TARGETLANGUAGE] ENGLISH
[PROMPT]
GPT, I would like to ask you a multi-part query. Please respond with "Next" after each input. When I type "PROCEED", generate a response taking into account all the previous parts of the query.
Example:
User: PART 1: [Enter the first part of the query here]
GPT: Next
User: PART 2: [Enter the second part of the query here]
GPT: Next
User: PART 3: [Enter the third part of the query here]
GPT: Next
...
User: PROCEED
GPT: [Response to all previously mentioned parts of the query]
title: Logner promt - next + proceed
